  <!-- MOPX 207 Operation -->
  <h2 id="operation">Operation</h2>
  <p>
    The <a href="https://www.alfalaval.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Alfa Laval</a> MOPX 207 Centrifuge is a self-cleaning, <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">disc-stack centrifuge</a> ideal for the continuous, three-phase separation of fuels and mineral oils.
  </p>
  <p>
    With a <strong>7.5 HP Motor</strong>, the MOPX 207 centrifuge has a bowl RPM of <strong>6,325</strong> and can process <strong>32 GPM of Distillate</strong>.
  </p>
  <p>
    The Alfa Laval MOPX-207 is a versatile, 'self-cleaning' centrifuge that is small enough to be manually serviced without the need for lifting devices (cranes, hoists, etc.)
  </p>
  <p>
    However, it can process over 30 Gallons per Minute of condensate.
  </p>

  <figure class="not-prose">
    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-mopx-207-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-MOPX207-Used-Oil-Centrifuge-600.webp"
      alt="Alfa Laval MOPX207 Used Oil Centrifuge"
      width="450"
      height="450"
      loading="lazy"
      class="img-cap-400"
    />
    <figcaption>Alfa Laval MOPX207 Used Oil Centrifuge</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <!-- MOPX Applications -->
  <h2 id="applications-mopx">Applications</h2>
  <p>
    The MOPX-207 finds a variety of applications in fuel and lubrication purification applications. Some of the popular applications are:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/diesel-fuel-purifier/">Diesel Fuel</a></li>
    <li><a href="/waste-oil-centrifuge/">Waste Oil</a></li>
    <li><a href="/black-diesel-centrifuge/">Black Diesel</a></li>
    <li><a href="/wvo-centrifuge-separator/">WVO or Yellow Grease</a></li>
    <li><a href="/biodiesel-centrifuge/">Biodiesel Glycerol</a></li>
    <li><a href="/fuel-oil-centrifuge/">Heavy Fuel Oil</a></li>
    <li><a href="/machine-coolant-centrifuge/">Machining Coolant</a></li>
    <li><a href="/quench-oil-centrifuge/">Quenching Oil</a></li>
    <li><a href="/crude-oil-centrifuge/">Light Crude Oil</a></li>
  </ul>

