  <h2 id="wspx-207">Alfa Laval WSPX 207 TGP Partial-Discharge <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">Disc-Stack Centrifuge</a></h2>
  <p>
    The Alfa Laval WSPX 207 Centrifuge is a self-cleaning disc-stack centrifuge designed for the three-phase concentration of water-based liquids such as machine coolants and washer liquids.
  </p>
  <p>
    With a <strong>7.5 HP Motor</strong>, the <strong>WSPX 207</strong> centrifuge has a <strong>bowl RPM of 6,400</strong> and can <strong>process 20 GPM</strong> of water-based <strong>machining coolant</strong>.
  </p>

  <figure class="not-prose">
