  <p>
    The Alfa Laval WSPX-207 is very similar to the WHPX-407, except that this centrifuge is a <strong>concentrator</strong>. A concentrator centrifuge is designed to separate a small oil volume from a large volume of water or water-based fluid. Some of the popular applications are:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/machining-coolant-recovery-centrifuge/">Machining Coolant</a></li>
